quran[6{c,v,t}:
9,94,"tum jab palat kar un ke paas pohncho ge to yeh terhan terhan ke azraat paish karen ge magar tum saaf keh dena ke"" bahanay nah karo, hum tumhari kisi baat ka aitbaar nah karen ge Allah ne hum ko tumahray halaat bta diye hain ab Allah aur is ka rasool tumahray tarz amal ko dekhe ga phir tum is ki taraf palta-ay jao ge jo khulay aur chupay sab ka jan-nay wala hai aur woh tumhe bta day ga ke tum kya kuch karte rahay ho """
9,95,"tumhari wapsi par yeh tumahray samnay kasmain khayen ge taakay tum un se sirf nazar karo to be shak tum un se sirf nazar hi kar lau, kyunkay yeh gandagi hain aur un ka asli maqam jahannum hai jo un ki kamaai ke badlay mein inhen naseeb hogi"
9,96,yeh tumahray samnay kasmain khayen ge ke taakay tum un se raazi ho jao halaank agar tum un se raazi ho bhi gay to Allah hargiz aisay fasik logon se raazi nah hoga
9,97,yeh badwi arab kufar o nifaq mein ziyada sakht hain aur un ke maamla mein is amar ke imkanaat ziyada hain ke is deen ke hudood se na waaqif rahen jo Allah ne apne rasool par nazil kya hai Allah sab kuch jaanta hai aur hakeem o Dana hai
9,98,unbadwiyonmein aisay aisay log mojood hain jo raah khuda mein kuch kharch karte hain to usay apne oopar zabardasti ki chti samajte hain aur tumahray haq mein zamana ki gardishon ka intzaar kar rahay hain ( ke tum kisi chakkar mein phanso tuwoh apni gardan se is nizaam ki itaat ka qladah utaar phankein jis mein tum ne inhen kis diya hai ) halaank badi ka chakkar khud unhi par musallat hai aur Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai
9,99,"aur unhi dabwiyonmein kuch log aisay bhi hain jo Allah aur roz aakhir par imaan rakhtay hain aur jo kuch kharch karte hain ussay Allah ke taqarab ka aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki taraf se rehmat ki duayen lainay ka zareya banatay hain haan! woh zaroor un ke liye taqarab ka zareya hai aur Allah zaroor un ko apni rehmat mein daakhil karega, yaqeenan Allah dar guzar karne wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
